{
  "stem": "1338.6",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Every day after work, I would wash up, and I would go out with a suit.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I didn't want anything to do with people in-- in leather jackets, and boots, and refugee kind of a style.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I wanted to be a normal person.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It became an obsession with me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I wanted to be normal.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I was.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I caught up on all the movies, as I said.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And it was wonderful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I waited for communication to open.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And the first thing they did is in July they opened the wire services to both the Soviet Union and the United States.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And since I knew that my uncle lived in Oklahoma in a small town, Carnegie.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "If you drive through Carnegie very fast, you can miss it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I mean, it's 2,000 population.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And so obviously, he was there for 60 years or 50 years, whatever it was, since 1905 or 1908.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "So obviously it was no problem, just write down Abe Grad, Carnegie, Oklahoma.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "So I did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I wrote a wire to him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I also remembered that my father had very prominent relatives in Moscow.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Because after the war, I'll have to go back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Historically, remember, the Russians and the Germans made an agreement.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "This is what made World War II possible.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "So they actually wrote us letters and sent us packages for the first two years when we were in Poland, in-- in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And even in ghetto, we were getting packages from-- from Soviet Union.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "But-- so I wrote to him, and I never got an answer.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "Obviously, now I know why.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "You don't communicate with-- with relatives outside of the Soviet Union.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
